Document: OpenXRCompositionLayerCylinder
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrcompositionlayercylinder.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the OpenXRCompositionLayerCylinder class.

- aspect_ratio (float): Controls the aspect ratio of the cylinder. Default: 1.0
- central_angle (float): Defines the central angle of the cylinder in radians. Default: 1.5707964
- fallback_segments (int): Specifies the number of segments to use if the cylinder cannot be rendered with higher detail. Default: 10
- radius (float): Sets the radius of the cylinder. Default: 1.0
