Document: OpenXRCompositionLayerCylinder  
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrcompositionlayercylinder.rst  
Summary: Properties and their descriptions for the OpenXRCompositionLayerCylinder class, including default values and setter/getter methods.  

aspect_ratio (float): The aspect ratio of the slice. Used to set the height relative to the width. Default: 1.0. Setter: set_aspect_ratio(float) → void. Getter: get_aspect_ratio() → float.  
central_angle (float): The central angle of the cylinder. Used to set the width. Default: 1.5707964. Setter: set_central_angle(float) → void. Getter: get_central_angle() → float.  
fallback_segments (int): The number of segments to use in the fallback mesh. Default: 10. Setter: set_fallback_segments(int) → void. Getter: get_fallback_segments() → int.  
radius (float): The radius of the cylinder. Default: 1.0. Setter: set_radius(float) → void. Getter: get_radius() → float.